{"tid":1980283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍：完全沒考慮减少對WHO的金援","createTime":"2020-04-20T03:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T06:03:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd67bf8d006b574454fb1702997cd34ad68decd","tid":1980283,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/04/20/phpW35Lgc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F20%2FphpW35Lgc.jpg&h=254fa924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n針對美國總統川普於上週宣佈暫時中斷對世界衛生組織（WHO）金援的舉措，日本首相安倍晋三表示看法，稱日本完全沒有考慮要減少對WHO的資金支持，並強調「必須支持WHO」。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於武漢肺炎疫情全球大流行，川普譴責WHO對武漢肺炎疫情的早期預警表現消極，害得全球錯失防疫良機、上萬人無端送命，此外也對WHO的運營偏向中國感到不滿。因此於上週二（4月14日）正式宣佈，暫時中斷對WHO的金援，直到WHO「檢討反省並改革」為止。<br />\n<br />\n《日經中文網》報導，在川普宣佈中斷WHO金援後，安倍晋三對此發表其看法，表示「完全沒有考慮減少日本的分擔金額」，並認為在當前疫情肆虐之際，必須支持WHO。<br />\n<br />\n而對於WHO運營偏向中國的觀點，安倍指出，此觀點也是事實，並認為在此波疫情平息後，應對WHO職能進行充分驗證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139245&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=267296c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3139245&h=3d5ac7e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3139245</a>"},{"pid":"e877c3b87cf0b5a508a7f159ec89442927610a8c","tid":1980283,"uid":220985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 垃圾"},{"pid":"66968fc4a5ff8193b220a2660c1a64d99339ac19","tid":1980283,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"Trump快d開返個新既，咁咪唔駛大家捐得咁委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":